<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Chess Game</title>
    <style type="text/css">
        .clickable {
            cursor: pointer;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <form id="form" action="chessRoom">
        <input id="roomId" name="roomId" hidden/>
    </form>
    <ul id="rooms"> 방 목록
        {{#chessRooms}}
            <li class="clickable">{{roomId}}</li>
        {{/chessRooms}}
        {{^chessRooms}}
            <li>방이 없습니다! 새 게임을 눌러 방을 만들어주세요.</li>
        {{/chessRooms}}
    </ul>
    <button id="newRoom" type="button">새 게임</button>
    <script type="text/javascript" src="js/main.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
